{"tid":53847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[恥笑369]【西方滲透？】強國大學禁慶聖誕 學生被逼睇孔子片","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T03:33:57.000Z","uid":987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4da6e1b4a69f0008f7690794f7a503195e698203","tid":53847,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161225/large/1482636899_4b45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161225%2Flarge%2F1482636899_4b45.jpg&h=28883648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普天同慶的聖誕節，但極重意識形態的強國則不在此限！陝西省西安市西北大學的學生稱，校方指聖誕節是「媚俗西方洋節」、「西方文化擴張」，不但嚴禁學生慶祝，更逼學生觀看孔子等各類中華傳統文化宣傳片，為防有學生偷偷狂歡，更有老師在各課室把守，「誰過聖誕就給誰處分」。<br />\n<br />\n「沒辦法啊，我們逃不出去！」有學生指出，在校內各處都掛着橫額，稱「爭做華夏優秀兒女，反對媚俗西方洋節」「抵禦西方文化擴張」等，學生稱昨晚平安夜，校方組織學生觀看中華傳統文化宣傳片，看宣傳片時，每個班級的輔導員都在場，樓下有許多老師把守，逃走將按平時三次曠課處理。<br />\n另一學生稱，每年的聖誕節，同學間沒有送蘋果、聚餐等傳統，「學校是封閉式管理，除了學習，我們只能待在宿舍玩電腦」。<br />\n而在浙江溫州一間小學，則收到來自教育局發來手機短信，要求「不在校園舉行任何與聖誕主題有關的活動和慶典」，小學校長稱過往英語老師牽頭，學生自願組織一些慶祝聖誕節的活動，學生表演節目，一起分零食，但收到通知後今年這類活動都被取消。<img src=\"http://staticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com/web_images/layout/art_end.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstaticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fweb_images%2Flayout%2Fart_end.gif&h=10b8c7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161225/large/1482636900_634a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161225%2Flarge%2F1482636900_634a.jpg&h=6766b183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c8d541b3a1d8bdeecd22a408f9598b23651434","tid":53847,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773870f7e1badc29ba70a1afa0de3a5de35e6fd6","tid":53847,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"萬聖節呢？"},{"pid":"9d88c5edfdea7240d6929383b09cfe6dcd84ffff","tid":53847,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"只準高官用洋貨<br />\n不準平民放聖誕<br />\n地獄鬼國-支那"},{"pid":"c31b7f85ad2dda16365edcc820d25cf636c880db","tid":53847,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"梵帝崗仲要同呢D國家建交。耶撚點睇?"},{"pid":"83a1cfa77e36c40335ff921fbfb6fe1a135e9ff0","tid":53847,"uid":61397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"又覺得西方文化擴張又